Title: Population 25
Writer: Craig Johnson (book), Hunt Baldwin (developer), John Coveny (developer), Hunt Baldwin, John Coveny
Actors: Robert Taylor, Katee Sackhoff, Lou Diamond Phillips, Bailey Chase
Plot: After a car accident, Vic and her husband Sean are captured by a survivalist who is also a suspect connected with sheriff Longmire's wife's murder, and Longmire is forced to work with Ed Gorski to get them out.
